title: Heather Presh was attacked by P. Swarm after he raised Eiben's price?
subtitle: A sarcastic article written by the Lord stated that Milan, Executive Director Heather Presh, was under the influence of bees and had a sensitive reaction.
author: Bethania Palma
vclaim: "Milan, CEO Heather Presh, as a bee squadron attacked her while he was wandering around the park, and no one nearly had Eppy Penn in hand to help her because she was too expensive."
